COMMENTS TO AUTHOR:  (Please use additional sheet(s) if necessary)

The paper proposes a framework to develop application-oriented communication
system. The proposed framework approach is interesting and can deliver a wide 
range of applications with the communication services they need.
The paper needs to elaborate more on the attributes and the mechanisms that
must be implemented to accommodate application requirements; for example what 
type of multi-cast algorithms, type of flow or error control,etc.

